name: IPhone
description: The iPhone has a camera and a music player (equivalent to the iPod), as well as software to send and receive text and voice messages

name: HP EliteBook Dragonfly G3
description: The HP EliteBook Dragonfly G3 is, as its name suggests, like a dragonfly: aerodynamic, ultralight, resistant and technologically designed for productivity

name: Gigabyte Aorus G5
description: Gigabyte Aorus G5 KC-5ES1130SD is a powerful mid-range device with a 15-inch IPS LED screen and Full HD resolution, with a 144 Hz refresh rate

name: Acer TravelMate
description: This Acer TravelMate P2 TMP214-53 is a device for productivity and multimedia use, with a 14-inch Full HD screen, although it is not especially light

name: Tv X14313
description: Medion X14313 is a smart TV modest in features, from the entry range, although with a 43-inch diagonal and 4K resolution on a 60 Hz LED LCD panel

name: LG Oled Flex
description: The LG OLED Flex is a 42-inch smart television, with 4K resolution, 120 Hz refresh rate and OLED technology. The panel arrives covered with a fairly effective anti-reflective coating, compatibility with NVIDIA's G-Sync and AMD Freesync technologies
